3021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T20:35:36.000Z","msg":"大食物盒加個鎖"},{"pid":"0fd3519c9d799ae809865041f6e0de64a6b4dfb5","tid":874860,"uid":128210,"like":3,"dislike":46,"score":-43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T20:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/043818_2ea406b1b51b07adb04fae5ec7eb8e8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F043818_2ea406b1b51b07adb04fae5ec7eb8e8e.jpg&h=9aebd18b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可冷藏可保溫。<br />\n車用電都得。<br />\n擺到6罐可樂。<br />\n擺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔到</span>市面大部分樽裝茶。<br />\n量好尺寸，去ikea 買個合用的食物盒，食唔晒的野先擺。<br />\n<br />\n駛鬼同人鬥心理。<br />\n<br />\n稍為唔好的係，用慣個細雪櫃，去超市買野飲，都係睇擺唔擺到落雪櫃先買。<br />\n<br />\nPs. 請預留散熱空間。"},{"pid":"4485cac44b264405a932fc935271b71fe8da93e1","tid":874860,"uid":33874,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"8a4cec81f8c2eaeb907f6102bbd502df3e17e917","tid":874860,"uid":104658,"like":420,"dislike":2,"score":418,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T13:48:30.000Z","msg":"痾啲尿落個玻璃餐盒到 加啲魚膠粉  <br />\n雪凍佢<br />\n扮整菠蘿味啫哩  <br />\n最好放一兩嚿菠蘿肉落去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T20:56:42.000Z","msg":"一打開好撚臭，鼻塞都知啦<br />\n尿係行唔通，除左裝忌廉，搏佢一開即飲"},{"pid":"a80d8a00145b5f6935769325e231d524525260bf","tid":874860,"uid":4526,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T21:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7mXie3J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7mXie3J.png&h=262681db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59069d57622e276f31cd364156031f695d16bf46","tid":874860,"uid":154753,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T21:59:45.000Z","msg":"貼保安個名落去"},{"pid":"ac5044bb6378063e175cdd16c3618b8a83681fea","tid":874860,"uid":76877,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T22:37:54.000Z","msg":"寫住勿jam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa41